<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="b19Jul1935"><font color="red">19 July 1935</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Harriet Weaver): Of the second part the section of plays is finished. The greater part of the lessons has just come out in Transition. It leaves two sections to be done &mdash; the stories (one or two of which are ready) and the going to sleep.  </div>
